<text id="02-output-contract" title="Laravel PHPUnit / Pest Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema for the test-plan manifest this methodology produces. Validator enforces required keys + per-field constraints.</summary>

  <section title="Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/php-phpunit-testing.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["framework", "test_dbms", "test_classes", "coverage_min", "gate_enforced_in_ci"],
  "properties": {
    "framework": {"enum": ["pest", "phpunit"]},
    "test_dbms": {"enum": ["postgres", "mysql", "sqlite"]},
    "test_classes": {
      "type": "array",
      "minItems": 1,
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["name", "layer", "uses_refresh_database"],
        "properties": {
          "name": {"type": "string"},
          "layer": {"enum": ["feature", "unit"]},
          "uses_refresh_database": {"type": "boolean"}
        }
      }
    },
    "coverage_min": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 80},
    "gate_enforced_in_ci": {"type": "boolean", "const": true},
    "forbidden_patterns_found": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "string"}, "maxItems": 0}
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "framework": "pest",
  "test_dbms": "postgres",
  "test_classes": [
    {"name": "Tests\\Feature\\Api\\UserCreateTest", "layer": "feature", "uses_refresh_database": true},
    {"name": "Tests\\Unit\\Services\\InvoiceCalculatorTest", "layer": "unit", "uses_refresh_database": false}
  ],
  "coverage_min": 82,
  "gate_enforced_in_ci": true,
  "forbidden_patterns_found": []
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "framework": "codeception",
  "test_dbms": "sqlite",
  "test_classes": [{"name": "FeatureUserTest", "layer": "feature", "uses_refresh_database": false}],
  "coverage_min": 40,
  "gate_enforced_in_ci": false,
  "forbidden_patterns_found": ["Mail::fake() called after $this->postJson(...)"]
}
]]></code>
    <note>Wrong framework; sqlite while prod is Postgres; Feature without RefreshDatabase; coverage below floor; CI gate off; fake placed after action.</note>
  </example>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <list>
      <item>Unit test extending `Tests\TestCase` (which boots Laravel).</item>
      <item>`Mail::fake()` / `Queue::fake()` called AFTER the action under test.</item>
      <item>`assertJsonStructure(['data' =&gt; ['id']])` used as a value check.</item>
      <item>Feature test touching DB without `RefreshDatabase`.</item>
      <item>`sleep(...)` inside a test method.</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-php-phpunit-testing.py">Validator script</reference>
</text>
